subject: Colleges and Universities
Basketball
Deaths (Obituaries)
lead_paragraph: Mr. Dambrot was a basketball star who led City College to the 1950 N.I.T. and N.C.A.A. titles, only to be engulfed in a national point-shaving scandal.
